# Folder Structure

## IdleTowerCore Package (Platform-Independent Game Logic)
Pure game logic that MUST NOT import SpriteKit, SwiftUI, or UIKit.
Can be reused across platforms (iOS app, TestHarness, etc.).

/ IdleTowerCore
  / Sources/IdleTowerCore
    - GameState.swift      # Saveable game state
    - Catalog.swift        # Game data definitions
    - Simulator.swift      # Core simulation logic
    - Economy.swift        # Cost curves and economy math
    - Card.swift           # Card system
    - Research.swift       # Research system

## IdleTower App (iOS-Specific Code)

/ IdleTower
  / Core                    # Platform-specific utilities
    / Sim
      - OfflineProgress.swift  # iOS offline progress calculation
    / Util
      - Persistence.swift      # iOS file I/O helpers
    / Model                   # (Currently empty - models live in IdleTowerCore)
  
  / Game
    / UI                     # SpriteKit UI components
    / Debug                  # Debug UI and controls
    - GameScene.swift        # Main game scene
    - GameViewController.swift
